<div id="header">
<h1>Scientific stagnation</h1>
</div>
<div id="content">
<div id="TOC"><ul>
<li><a href="#background">Background</a></li>
<li><a href="#diminishing-marginal-returns">Diminishing marginal returns</a></li>
<li><a href="#science">Science</a><ul>
<li><a href="#cost">Cost</a></li>
<li><a href="#benefit">Benefit</a></li>
</ul></li>
<li><a href="#commercialization">Commercialization</a><ul>
<li><a href="#pharmaceuticals">Pharmaceuticals</a></li>
</ul></li>
<li><a href="#todo">TODO</a></li>
<li><a href="#china">China</a><ul>
<li><a href="#education">Education</a></li>
<li><a href="#rd">R&amp;D</a></li>
